fly away home ( a.k.a. flying wild and father goose ) is a 1996 family comedy-drama film directed by carroll ballard .   the film stars anna paquin , jeff daniels and dana delany .   fly away home was released on september 13 , 1996 by columbia pictures .   fly away home dramatizes the actual experiences of bill lishman who , in 1986 , started training canadian geese to follow his ultralight aircraft , and succeeded in leading their migration in 1993 through his program " operation migration . "   the film is also based on the experience of dr. william j.l. sladen , a british-born zoologist and adventurer , who aided lishman with the migration .